This is my first mini game map so please be gently.  I took a bunch of prefabs and some ideas and made them into weapons inspired by spearwars.  You spawn with nothing and you grab an item(with a knife) and most likely, the front is the killer part trying to stab your oppenents.  But i must warn there will probably be TKing since people are idiots
